column2: select   ObjID, ra, dec, G.z,  specobj.plate as specobj_plate, specobj.mjd as specobj_mjd,     specobj.fiberid as specobj_fiberid,   modelMag_u-modelMag_r, modelMag_r-modelMag_z,   modelMag_g, modelMag_i    from Galaxy  where modelMag_u-modelMag_r < # AND   modelMag_r-modelMag_z < # AND   modelMag_u-modelMag_r > # + # * modelMag_r-modelMag_z
